CustomField.description: The API name of a custom field set used by the Milestone object. This field set defines the milestone from opportunity product columns that are read only during creation of a project from an opportunity using a template. No default field set is defined.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name of a custom field set used by the Milestone object. This field set defines the milestone from opportunity product columns that are read only during creation of a project from an opportunity using a template. No default field set is defined.
CustomField.label: Milestone Opp Product (Tmpl) Read Only
